"""Kestrel — efficient local MoE runtime.

  kestrel build              build engine/kestrel-engine
  kestrel doctor             RAM / install checks
  kestrel plan [--ram N]     resource plan for a model dir
  kestrel chat --model DIR   interactive generate
  kestrel serve --model DIR  OpenAI-compatible /v1 (+ Library API)
  kestrel pull MODEL_ID      download catalog model into ~/.kestrel/models
  kestrel bench              fair without-vs-with Kestrel bench + verify
  kestrel app                serve Library+Chat UI + API
  kestrel oracle             TF 32/32 self-test on fixtures/glm_tiny
"""
